OL,3,CSuspect charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cof Rihanna
OL,6,FA 35-year-old woman accused of
OL,7,Fallegedly firing gunshots at the Los
OL,8,FAngeles home of singer Rihanna has
OL,9,Fbeen charged with attempted murder.
OL,11,FIvanna Lisette Ortiz from Florida was
OL,12,Falso charged with 10 counts of assault
OL,13,Fon a person with a semiautomatic
OL,14,Ffirearm and three counts of shooting
OL,15,Fat an inhabited vehicle or dwelling,
OL,16,Flocal officials said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
