PN,31302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773256285
OL,3,CSuspect charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cof Rihanna
OL,6,FIt is alleged that Ms Ortiz drove to
OL,7,Fthe home of Rihanna and her family on
OL,8,FSunday afternoon and fired a
OL,9,Fsemiautomatic weapon multiple times at
OL,10,Fthe residence.
OL,12,FNo one was injured during the incident.
OL,14,FHochman said Rihanna (Robin Fenty),
OL,15,Fher partner rapper A$AP Rocky (Rakim
OL,16,FMayers), their three children, and
OL,17,FRihanna's mother were all on the
OL,18,Fproperty at the time of the incident.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
