PN,31303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773256285
OL,3,CSuspect charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cof Rihanna
OL,6,FHe said Rihanna and her partner were
OL,7,Ftogether in a trailer on the property
OL,8,Fat the time of the shooting, whilst
OL,9,Fother family members and staff were
OL,10,Finside the house.
OL,12,F"Opening fire in any populated
OL,13,Fneighbourhood is extremely dangerous,
OL,14,Fputs lives at risk and will be fully
OL,15,Fprosecuted," Hochman said in a
OL,16,Fstatement.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
