FL,314,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773256285
OL,3,CSuspect charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cof Rihanna
OL,6,F"Thankfully, no one was injured in
OL,7,Fthis shooting, but this careless
OL,8,Fviolence will not be tolerated in our
OL,9,Fcommunity. Such shooters will find
OL,10,Ftheir next destination to be our jails
OL,11,Fand prisons."
OL,13,FInside the court, Ortiz's attorney,
OL,14,FDeputy Public Defender Jamarcus
OL,15,FBradford, at first entered a plea of
OL,16,Fnot guilty on her behalf, but then
OL,17,Fwithdrew it in favour of postponing
OL,18,Fthe arraignment until March 25.
OL,20,FShe is being held on a $1.8 million
OL,21,Fbail (around #1.3 million).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
