PN,31305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773256285
OL,3,CSuspect charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cof Rihanna
OL,6,FBradford did not speak to reporters
OL,7,Foutside of court.
OL,9,FThe LA County Public Defender's Office
OL,10,Fsaid in a statement that it could not
OL,11,Fcomment on the pending case against
OL,12,FOrtiz.
OL,14,F"As in every case, we will work to
OL,15,Fensure that our client receives the
OL,16,Ffull protections guaranteed under the
OL,17,FConstitution," the statement said.
OL,19,FIf convicted on all charges, Ortiz
OL,20,Fcould get life in prison.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
