OL,3,CSuspect charged with attempted murder
OL,4,Cof Rihanna
OL,6,FJudge Theresa McGonigle issued a
OL,7,Fprotection order for Ortiz to stay
OL,8,Faway from Rihanna and her partner, as
OL,9,Fwell as their home.
OL,11,FShe also added that Ortiz is not
OL,12,Fallowed to possess any firearms or
OL,13,Fammunition, along with several other
OL,14,Fconditions.
